Package: Ramses
Type: Package
Title: R Package for Antimicrobial Stewardship & Surveillance 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Peter",
           family = "Dutey",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "p.dutey-magni@ucl.ac.uk",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8942-9836"))
Description: Ramses is a one-stop shop for antimicrobial stewardship data warehousing for hospitals. 
    It supports the modelling and analysis of hospital electronic health records 
    (episode of care, prescriptions, administration, pathology and investigations) to help
    keep antibiotics working for years to come.
